client.control

Class ExaminationController

  • java.lang.Object
    • client.control.ExaminationController
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IController, javafx.fxml.Initializable

    public class ExaminationController
extends java.lang.Object
implements IController, javafx.fxml.Initializable
    ExaminationController is the Controller to the gui of the viewreference by the LabWorker , the Labworker can see all the details of any reference he chose by date,specialist id, client id or by reference number.

    Raz
